description: Welcome to 606 East 8th Street, Unit 1, a modern and elegant 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom home in South Boston. This residence boasts a chef's kitchen, with an open kitchen layout, and hardwood floors throughout. Enjoy the convenience of a washer/dryer in unit and a deck with direct access to a turfed backyard, perfect for soaking up the summer sun! Additionally, take advantage of the large basement/storage area, ideal for a home gym or extra space to suit your needs. Not to mention, you're just a stone's throw from M Street Beach and a variety of amazing restaurants. Discover the ease of city living - come see it for yourself!
